        <strong>Step 3 — Interview coaching</strong>
        <span>We prepare you for the hardest interview question every career changer faces: "Why are you making this transition?" — and for the function-specific questions you will face once you are in the room.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="location-card">
        <strong>Step 4 — Targeting strategy</strong>
        <span>We identify which companies, teams, and roles are most receptive to career changers with your background — so your applications land where they have the highest conversion probability.</span>
